snippet.title: Command & Conquer 4 Trailer
snippet.description:
Command & Conquer is back with C&C 4, the fourth and final chapter in the epic Tiberium saga. 

With humanity on the verge of extinction due to the ever expanding Tiberium threat, GDI is deep into its darkest hour. 

Just when extinction seems completely imminent, a surprise visit from an old friend reveals a potential cure for Earths plight. Who is this mysterious visitor, and what exactly does he want in return for mankinds salvation? 

Watch the trailer to find out!
